 286:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_gpio.c **** /**
 287:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_gpio.c ****   * @brief  De-initialize the GPIOx peripheral registers to their default reset values.
